=== Television === {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" |- style="background:#ccc; text-align:center;" !scope="col"| Year !scope="col"| Title !scope="col"| Role !scope="col"| Notes ! scope="col" class="unsortable" | {{Tooltip|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}} |- |2007 |''Kalaa Dheke Varah Loabivey'' |Yumna |Main role | style="text-align: center;"| |- |2007-2008 |''Vimlaa'' |Reema |Recurring role | style="text-align: center;"| |- | 2008 | ''[[Soora]]'' | Zeena | Main role; 5 Episodes | style="text-align: center;"| <ref name=soora/> |- |2008 |''Kushakaanulaa Shazaa Nudheyshey'' | |Main role | style="text-align: center;"| |- |2008 |''Asarugai...'' | |Main role; 5 Episodes | style="text-align: center;"| |- |2012 |''[[Dhirumeh Nethas]]'' |Noora |Recurring role; 5 Episodes | style="text-align: center;"| |- |2012 |''Vaudhey Mee'' |Hudha |Main role; 13 Episodes | style="text-align: center;"| |- |}
